      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative specimen of the S54B32 powertrain, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-compression ratio that yields a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure torsional rigidity, while the double-VANOS system has been overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Every bushing and suspension component remains in factory-new tolerance, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are renowned for. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting its pampered, climate-controlled history.",
