    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality 2019 sports sedan that defines the 'mint' standard. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Every body panel is original with perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition, retaining that distinct new-car aroma. The premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since day one. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It features a comprehensive service history exclusively through authorized dealerships, with all fluids recently flushed and high-performance tires showing near-full tread depth. This sale includes the original window sticker, two keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
